  "codeChangesMessage": "Migrate database layer from Oracle to PostgreSQL",
  "codeChangesDetails": "- Replace Oracle JDBC driver (ojdbc11) with PostgreSQL JDBC driver (org.postgresql:postgresql)\n  - Removed com.oracle.database.jdbc:ojdbc11 from pom.xml\n  - Added org.postgresql:postgresql (managed by Spring Boot BOM) to pom.xml\n  - Added com.azure:azure-identity-extensions:1.2.2 for passwordless Azure connection\n- Update application.properties from Oracle to PostgreSQL datasource\n  - Changed JDBC URL to PostgreSQL with managed identity passwordless authentication\n  - Changed driver-class-name from oracle.jdbc.OracleDriver to org.postgresql.Driver\n  - Changed JPA dialect from OracleDialect to PostgreSQLDialect\n  - Added service principal authentication example URL\n- Update application-docker.properties from Oracle to PostgreSQL datasource\n  - Changed JDBC URL to jdbc:postgresql://postgres-db:5432/photoalbum with env var defaults\n  - Changed driver and dialect to PostgreSQL equivalents\n  - Used POSTGRES_USERNAME/POSTGRES_PASSWORD env vars\n- Update application-test.properties for H2 in PostgreSQL mode\n  - Changed H2 URL to include MODE=PostgreSQL;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1\n- Migrate Photo.java entity from Oracle to PostgreSQL\n  - Removed @Lob annotation from photoData field (Oracle BLOB → PostgreSQL bytea)\n  - Added columnDefinition=\"bytea\" to photo_data @Column annotation\n  - Removed Oracle-specific columnDefinition=\"NUMBER(19,0)\" from file_size\n  - Replaced columnDefinition=\"TIMESTAMP DEFAULT SYSTIMESTAMP\" with TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP for uploaded_at\n- Migrate PhotoRepository.java native SQL queries from Oracle to PostgreSQL\n  - findAllOrderByUploadedAtDesc: lowercased all table/column names\n  - findPhotosUploadedBefore: replaced ROWNUM-based subquery with LIMIT 10\n  - findPhotosUploadedAfter: replaced NVL() with COALESCE(), lowercased identifiers\n  - findPhotosByUploadMonth: replaced TO_CHAR() with EXTRACT(YEAR/MONTH FROM ...)\n  - findPhotosWithPagination: replaced Oracle ROWNUM subquery with ROW_NUMBER() OVER window function\n  - findPhotosWithStatistics: lowercased all table/column names (RANK() and SUM() OVER are standard SQL)\n- Update docker-compose.yml from Oracle to PostgreSQL\n  - Replaced oracle-db service (gvenzl/oracle-free) with postgres-db service (postgres:16)\n  - Updated healthcheck, volumes, and environment variables for PostgreSQL"
}}).
